oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Senior Class of 1922
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Composite photograph of the 1922 Senior Class of Middle Tennessee State Normal School

Top row (left to right): Lela McDaniel; Hazel Smith. 2nd row: Laura Davis; Verda Broome; Nelle Moyers; Mildred Copehaver; William Keene; Leona Graham; Haskell Sims; Beulah Clark; Atla Patterson; Hobart Massey. 3rd row: Lucy Harris; Maymie Quandt; Mrs. Annie Rowe; Elizabell Leigh; Evelena Movers; William Beasley; Dixie Edwards; Victor Keene; Ruby Harris; Jane Hatchett. 4th row: H.C. Brier; Louise Glaus; Fred Brandon; Marion Poplin; Ralph Shelton; Margaret Sanders; Joe R. Thompson; Rebecca Hill; Herman McDonough; Hattie Lillian Wright. 5th row: Wesley P. Flatt; Blanche Cardy; Frank Bass; Claris M. Elmore (President); Esther Jackson (Vice President); Margarite Crick (Secretary); Terrell Twitty (Treasurer); Gladys Bond; Lena Pipkin; Kirby McKnight.
